{"tid":788343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解D人會讚成「台灣獨立」，但反對「西藏獨立」？","createTime":"2018-08-21T11:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T11:49:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc017a1a4342c67e117069fb457fb20b44763f0","tid":788343,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/release/release1543.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkupop.hku.hk%2Fchinese%2Frelease%2Frelease1543.html&d=L%2BH0bQRk4Pi11%2BTj%2ByuzkZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=16d37199\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/release/release1543.html</a><br />\n<br />\n贊成台灣重新加入聯合國比率 ... 54%<br />\n贊成台灣獨立比率 ... 33%<br />\n認為一國兩制適用於台灣的比率 ... 35%<br />\n贊成西藏獨立比率 ... 19%<br />\n<br />\n(我假設贊成台灣獨立既人, 先會有可能支持西藏獨立)<br />\n<br />\n贊成台灣獨立 - 贊成西藏獨立 = 14%<br />\n<br />\n究竟有乜原因, 呢14%人覺得台灣、西藏之間既分別導致後者唔應該獨立, 繼續被支那匪國迫害呢？"},{"pid":"709c5c3a8d5df900d21b72d86e9670e72ccb7bc8","tid":788343,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"因為台灣實際上已經獨立"}]}